{"tid":483204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解一直冇人屌支那人大常委會？","createTime":"2017-11-29T01:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T02:39:46.000Z","uid":142888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c9db929a17fd9a545c2f17d5d17e2f213d2988ec","tid":483204,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:54:57.000Z","msg":"明明佢哋先係近年香港混亂嘅根源，居然冇人屌過佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上次政改又係佢哋落閘 引發佔中，宣誓風波連袁國強都話唔需要人大釋法，但人大班支那豚慰安雞仍然釋法，一次又一次興風作浪，真係忍撚夠佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06120ed6b427d9aad6ec3773a81a04162c0249e2","tid":483204,"uid":142029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"樓主坐左幾耐?"},{"pid":"56ff075cef54dab64eadbf9411e30953ffae73b3","tid":483204,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:58:19.000Z","msg":"我地搞港獨已經好忙"},{"pid":"1a3534da0d301dbca68d0d301fc8709013b194ea","tid":483204,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主坐左幾耐?</blockquote><br />\n想屌好耐，不過懶得打千字文屌"},{"pid":"4917980d81449a34ca159c2b8c2e05ab5f54c1e1","tid":483204,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:05:29.000Z","msg":"其實朱凱迪之前冇錯，中晒point，但兩登小學雞笑尻佢<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/100501_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F100501_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=de70102e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/100522_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F100522_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=a43ba811&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33bee5a55846abee48d69438eb5264c171fcc8b3","tid":483204,"uid":90,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:05:55.000Z","msg":"屌支共同人大有咩大分別？"},{"pid":"b4d352cf4c066998c236aab0e45c4c31fa9609e1","tid":483204,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌支共同人大有咩大分別？</blockquote><br />\n支共都冇人屌啦，啲人只係識屌港共，明明支共同人大先係根源<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4e537e6b60739fda2e4a060082269746bc80a5","tid":483204,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d888c219bd79f10e02a54d2facc8a33381062dba","tid":483204,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地搞港獨已經好忙</blockquote><br />\n搞港獨冇撚用，又冇道德高地，彭定康都唔屌。反而屌人大濫權，可以有道德高地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實人大釋法要經終審法院要求先可以釋法"},{"pid":"8b6a905b5342e1da0fb639ddee885f550140290b","tid":483204,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T02:39:46.000Z","msg":"反中共已經一律反埋一切有關既野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}